1. $cd [your_favorite_directory]
   $ git clone ... zen-conding-rm-plugin
   $ cd zen-conding-rm-plugin
   $ svn checkout http://zen-coding.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/zen-coding-read-only

2. If you are using Ubuntu or MacOS go to 3)

   For Windows users:
   * Install python
   * Specify path to python executable in [your_favorite_directory]/zen-conding-rm-plugin/config.yml file

3. * Launch RubyMine
   * Open File | Settings | Extensions" dialog
   * Press "Add" button and specify [your_favorite_directory]/zen-conding-rm-plugin/ext folder
   * Press "Apply"
   * Relaunch RubyMine. 



